<collectingCountry id="B0F7E3C5FFB3FFAEFF13DEE6FEE727DE" box="[192,303,1155,1179]" name="Trinidad and Tobago" pageId="80" pageNumber="77">Trinidad</collectingCountry>
, but the latter species has both elytral spots highly irregular, the result of coalescing of normally discrete spots.
</paragraph>
